bgs.name: 02_狭山丘陵_森林ループ環境音

parameters: SetFrontLight -1 1 50

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](No... I don't have any business in the lesson
room)

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](I think it's rude to do this at this
time, but it's okay to talk a little,
right...)

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](No... Am I overthinking it? \N[5]-san
wouldn't get angry over something like
this, and besides...)

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](Yes... \N[5]-san always gives me the words I want the
most.)

\F[\V[2]]......It has always been like this. Whenever we
faced any problems, \N[5]-san would
always smile, listen to our concerns,
and guide us in the direction that felt
right.

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](I may be clueless when it comes to
romance... sigh... I've been making
quite an effort to appeal to him
though...)
\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](Hmm... I'm starting to get a little angry.)

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](Alright, even if he's sleeping, who cares! He's
the manager, right? It's only natural
for him to take care of my mental well-
being!)

I gather all my pent-up frustration and
take a step towards the door, determined
to knock on it with all my might.

However, just before that... in the silence
dominated by darkness, I faintly hear a
sound that is inappropriate in many
ways, and my whole body stiffens.

\F[\V[2]]I heard a seductive moan from a woman. As
my body stiffened, my strength gradually
faded away like receding waves.

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](No way... Could this be... \N[5]-san...? Huh? N-No, no way... Hold on a
second...)

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](First of all... There shouldn't be any other
women in the mansion right now. I
haven't confirmed it properly, but at
least I haven't met anyone.)
\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](But... beyond this door... no, wait...)
\F[\V[2]]......I suddenly feel a sense of déjà vu.

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](That's right... It's not necessarily a woman.
There's a possibility that \N[5]-san is
watching the very same footage that I've
seen multiple times...)

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](Actually, that possibility seems more likely.
Even if there were other women besides
me, he wouldn't be the kind of person to
bring a woman in at a time like this...)

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](If that's the case, it might be impossible
now. It would become awkward between
us...)

I lowered my arm that was about to knock
and took a step back.

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](I wonder what this misunderstanding is...
I just... wanted to meet and talk...)

I turned on my heel and left his room.
Come to think of it, that's always how
it's been between us. We never really
connect at the crucial moments, and
there's always a certain distance
between us.

Due to work circumstances, it can't be
helped... But today, I couldn't help but
feel a lingering attachment as I stopped
and turned around.

I wait... It's just selfish and self-
centered expectations.\!... But as
expected, the door to his room doesn't
open, and my faint hopes are
shattered----...
\.\SE[タイプライター]Ｎ\.\SE[タイプライター]Ｅ\.\SE[タイプライター]Ｘ\.\SE[タイプライター]Ｔ\. \SE[タイプライター]Ｄ\.\SE[タイプライター]Ａ\.\SE[タイプライター]Ｙ\.\SE[タイプライター]...
\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](...It's already empty.)

......It seems that the old key is not meant to
open this door.
......It seems that the door is locked.
......It seems that the door is locked.
